## THE ARCHITECTURE

```
AQARION Master System
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ üß† Multi-AI Consensus Layer
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Claude (reasoning, analysis)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ GPT-4 (creativity, generation)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Gemini (research, synthesis)
