‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Propose (each AI suggests approach)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Debate (AIs challenge each other)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Vote (weighted by expertise)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Synthesize (best of all approaches)
